title: #92Noon! Coyle/Florio/SaundersPresser/Trachsel/Titles
description: Charlie Coyle opens the show as he hunts a Stanley Cup with the Bruins, Florio's weekly spot to end the first hour, portions of the Ryan Saunders introductory presser as official Wolves coach, Gopher Softball coach Jamie Trachsel, and then some pondering as to which MN team winning a title would mean most to listeners.
